  "message": "test(conformance): add dtype promotion oracle fixture with 162 JAX-verified cases\n\nAdd dtype_promotion_oracle.v1.json with 162 dtype promotion cases\ncaptured from JAX covering all type pairs for result_dtype and\nlattice_promote. Add dtype_promotion_oracle_parity.rs test runner\nloading the fixture and asserting our promotion rules match JAX for\nall supported core types (32 cases passing). Update FEATURE_PARITY.md\nto reference the oracle fixture and test coverage.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
